#

Rotini with Tomato and Spinach

25 min
$8.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Quick MealPastaHealthy

Description

A quick and healthy pasta dish featuring rotini, fresh tomatoes, and spinach, perfect for a light yet satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • rotini pasta: 8 oz
  • fresh spinach: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 2 cups
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • red pepper flakes: optional
